📄 index.html — Line-by-Line Explanation:

<!DOCTYPE html> ( Declares the document type as HTML5.)


<html lang="en"> (Starts the HTML document and sets the language to English.)


<head> (Begins the head section (info about the webpage).


    <meta charset="UTF-8"> (Sets character encoding to support most symbols/text.)


    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> (Makes the website responsive for mobile
    devices.)


    <title>ATY WEB — Compare Smartly</title> (Sets the title that appears on the browser tab.)


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style/style.css"> (Links the external CSS file for styling.)


    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> (Loads a
    Google Font named "Inter" for modern text style.)


</head> (Ends the head section.)


<body> (Begins the visible content of the page.)


    <header> (Header section with project title and tagline.)
        <h1>🛒 ATY WEB</h1>
        <p>All Things You Need — Compared Smartly</p>
    </header>


    <main>
        <input type="text" id="link" placeholder="Paste Amazon product link..." /> (input: where users paste the product
        link.)
        <button onclick="fetchProduct()">Compare Prices</button> (button: triggers the comparison function.)
        <div id="result"></div> (div: where results will appear.)
    </main>



    <footer>
        <p>Made with ❤️ by <strong>VortexByte ~ Sanket Padhyal</strong></p> (Footer section with your name and version
        info.)
        <p class="small">CURRENTLY DEMO VERSION v1🙏</p>
    </footer>



    <script src="js/script.js"></script> (Links the JavaScript file that powers the app logic.)


</body> (Ends the body and HTML document.)

</html>
